					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near the Patel's house in the village.</p>						

						<p>1434 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1356, Ānanda, Mēsha Prathamā, Sunday.</hi> The details given correspond to <hi rend="bold">1434 A.D., March 27</hi> when the weekday was Saturday, not Sunday.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to a Jōgi-purusha called Jugādi-kuṇḍala by Jōgi Voḍeya <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Chavuṭa.</p>						

						</summary>
